Author: paperklipp
Text: Morning: 45-60 minute elliptical.   Afternoon: 40-60 minute yoga & dumbbells.   Evening: 120 minute outdoor walk.

Author: JuBelen
Text: I do 100 leg raises and 100 glute kickbacks everyday. Then I do something more depending on the day, I have some dumbbels so I do chest and head presses somedays, others I do squats. I also walk 3 to 6 km everyday.  I don't really know much about gym and working out I just do what feels good to me to release tension. I used to swim but I can't afford it anymore ($$$).
